summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting easements from The Housing Authority of the City of Seattle over portions of Section 27, Township 24 North, Range 4 East, W.M. portions of Lots 34, 36 and 37 Somerville Addition; portion of Block 3, Plouf's 2nd Addition; and portion of Holly Street in Airline Addition for storm drain purposes.
